trans-unit.source: Consists of a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects to be used with catalogs of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Består av en samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objekt som ska användas med kataloger med <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is created by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in their implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDescriptionCollection skapas av de olika <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller i sina implementeringar av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: For each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that is contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object is created.
trans-unit.target: För varje <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll som finns i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroll, en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objektet har skapats.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: This object maintains basic information about a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, including its ID, its title, its description, and a path to an associated icon.
trans-unit.target: Det här objektet innehåller grundläggande information om en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll, inklusive ID, dess rubrik, beskrivning och en sökväg till en associerad ikon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls can use a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to display a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control's information in the catalog, without having to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control itself.
trans-unit.target: De olika <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller kan använda en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt att visa en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollens information i katalogen, utan att behöva skapa en instans av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>själva.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is used internally by the Web Parts control set to maintain a collection of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects used in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDescriptionCollection används internt av kontrollen webbdelar som anger att underhålla en samling med alla de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt som används i en katalog.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection collection is used only when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen WebPartDescriptionCollection används bara när en sida i katalogen visningsläget.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is being rendered, it loops through the WebPartDescriptionCollection collection, adding the information from each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to the displayed catalog.
trans-unit.target: När en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontrollen återges, den loop genom samlingen WebPartDescriptionCollection att lägga till informationen från varje <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt som ska visas katalogen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny tom instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: This overload of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor can be used to create an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Den här överlagring för den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>konstruktorn kan användas för att skapa en tom samling.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control creates an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> object if the content of an imported description file is `null`.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>kontrollen skapar en tom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection>objekt om innehållet i en beskrivningsfil som importerade är `null`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> object by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> objekt genom att passera i en <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objekt.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection constructor is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method implementations within the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to create a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktorn WebPartDescriptionCollection används av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>implementeringar av metoden inom de olika <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>kontroller för att skapa en samling <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects that correspond to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: En samling <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> objekt som motsvarar den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller i en katalog.
